original_client_text.markup_text:
Chicken Parm Grilled Cheese Loaf
Ingredients below (serves 4, or 1 really hungry person)

INGREDIENTS
1 circular sourdough loaf
1 large chicken breast
4 eggs
1/2 cup Italian seasoning (divided in half)
1 cup flour
1 cup panko bread crumbs
1 cup grated parmesan cheese
4 slices mild cheddar
4 slices muenster cheese
4 slices mozzarella
1 cup marinara sauce
1/34 cup softened salted butter
1 head of roasted garlic
1/4 cup chopped parsley
2 cups cooking oil
